  "remarks": "FATER INSTITUTE was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: Entities owned, controlled, or acting on behalf of the Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps. Khatam al-Anbiya (KAA) subsidiary. Fater has worked with foreign suppliers, likely on behalf of other KAA companies on IRGC projects in Iran.\n\nThe Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
